_sText:
Its now about 1 year ago i was working with Hammer Editor...
I just thought i'll give it a try again and i had fun creating this map.
This is the result of 1 Week work (few hours every day)

I made this map to relearn working with the editor :]
it became a qality i thougt its ok to share.
all textures and sounds are default (no custom sounds/textures)

enjoy this adventure or have some speedruns :]
sorry for my bad english


EDIT: 25.01.15 retextured the grey/blue room to fix lagg problems
[redownload this map if u already have it, make sure to delete the old bhop_quep in your cstrike/maps folder!
